r%20whatever%20the%20case%20may%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20more%20women%20lately%20coming%20in.%20We%20don't%20take%20them%20all%20%E2%80%94%20we%20refer%20them%20out%20if%20they're%20not%20right%20for%20us.%20I%20don't%20take%20a%20client%20just%20because%20they%20come%20in.%20I%20have%20to%20see%20if%20I%20have%20the%20people%20that%20would%20be%20right%20for%20them.%20I'm%20very%20small.%20I'm%20not%20a%20big%20company.%20I'm%20very%20particular%2C%20but%20I%20work%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20matchmakers%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Destin%20Jude%20Pfaff%2C%20Patti%20Stanger%2C%20Chelsea%20Autumn%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Millionaire%20Matchmaker%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6616fb0b3f923f7dab0691a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStanger%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Millionaire%20Matchmaker.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEvans%20Vestal%20Ward%2FNBCU%20Photo%20Bank%2FNBCUniversal%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20mistakes%20you%20see%20ultrawealthy%20people%20make%20when%20they're%20dating%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20is%20to%20the%20floor.%20And%20because%20they're%20so%20cerebral%20in%20their%20head%20with%20business%2C%20they%20think%20that%20they%20can%20date%20like%20ordering%20a%20pizza%20where%20people%20are%20not%20pizzas.%20They%20have%20trauma%2C%20they%20have%20damage%2C%20they%20got%20baggage.%20And%20after%20the%20five%20non-negotiables%20and%20the%20two%20physical%20quirks%2C%20you've%20got%20to%20stop%20the%20list%20because%20the%20list%20is%20never%20going%20to%20be%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20quirkiness.%20They%20get%20to%20the%20point%20where%20they're%20in%20their%2060s%20and%20they're%20still%20going%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20wrong%20with%20me%3F%20Why%20didn't%20this%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20my%20friends%20who%20are%20in%20LA%20and%20big%20in%20business%2C%20they're%20in%20their%2040s%20and%2050s%20and%2060s%2C%20they%20either%20have%20been%20divorced%20or%20haven't%20gotten%20married%20and%20they%20still%20haven't%20found%20the%20right%20person.%20I%20heard%20Jennifer%20Aniston%20was%20saying%20recently%20that%20she%20was%20in%20seven%20years%20of%20dating%20hell%2C%20and%20I%20completely%20understand%20that.%20Her%20and%20Reese%20Witherspoon%2C%20the%20two%20people%20I'd%20love%20to%20meet%2C%20because%20I%20understand%20what%20they're%20going%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20women%20in%20LA%20are%20fine%20wine%20and%20men%20are%20intimidated%20by%20them.%20I%20had%20that%20in%20my%20last%20relationship.%20He%20literally%20wrote%20in%20a%20text%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20intimidated%20by%20your%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I%20didn't%20know%20it%20the%20whole%20time%20we%20were%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20was%20that%20relationship%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20lasted%20almost%20a%20year.%20We%20met%20on%20Tinder%2C%20believe%20it%20or%20not.%20But%20he's%20in%20another%20relationship%20now%20with%20a%20girl%20that%20doesn't%20make%20money.%20So%20it's%20better%20for%20him%20in%20his%20mind.%20But%20I%20didn't%20know%20that%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20times%20you're%20dating%20someone%20and%20they're%20not%20speaking%20up%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20you're%20male%2C%20female%2C%20gay%2C%20straight%20%E2%80%94%20and%20telling%20you%20what's%20bothering%20them%20because%20they're%20embarrassed.%20A%20lot%20of%20it's%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20interesting%20that%20you%20met%20your%20ex%20on%20a%20dating%20app.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20I%20have%20a%20very%20small%20company%20and%20I'm%20not%20really%20attracted%20to%20my%20clients.%20And%20I%20would%20never%20date%20them%20anyway.%20That%20is%20the%20first%20way%20to%20get%20into%20a%20lawsuit.%