nee%2C%20holding%20your%20balance%20in%20that%20position.%20You%20can%20also%20move%20side%20to%20side%20or%20add%20a%20quarter%20turn%20to%20make%20it%20more%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKwaipen%20said%20she's%20seen%20clients%20experience%20major%20health%20benefits%20from%20the%20exercise%20%E2%80%94%20one%20woman%20said%20doing%20the%20drill%20helped%20her%20avoid%20serious%20injury%20when%20her%20dog%20pulled%20her%20off%20balance%20to%20chase%20after%20a%20rabbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20my%20members%20emailed%20me%20and%20she%20says%2C%20'Andi%2C%20I%20just%20have%20to%20let%20you%20know%20I%20hate%20that%20step%2C%20quick%20hold.%20But%20let%20me%20tell%20you%20saved%20me.%20I%20didn't%20fall%20over%20because%20I%20had%20that%20ability%2C'%26quot%3B%20Kwapien%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20that%20I%20hope%20that%20you%20ever%20have%20that%20situation%2C%20but%20my%20hope%20is%20that%20the%20training%20is%20real%20life%20to%20what%20you%20need.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStability%20training%20is%20also%20great%20for%20building%20muscle%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimprove-mobility-build-muscle-longevity-exercise-personal-trainer-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotecting%20your%20joints%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20functional%20movements%20like%20step-ups%20and%20other%20single-leg%20exercises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20trainers%20also%20recommend%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcore-exercise-to-do-instead-of-planks-build-strong-abs-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPallof%20press%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20plank%20variations%20for%20a%20strong%20core.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStability%20can%20give%20you%20a%20challenging%20work%20out%2C%20too.%20More%20intense%20versions%20of%20stability%20exercises%20include%20movements%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-do-single-leg-pistol-squats-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle-leg%