0said%20the%20%26quot%3Bweak%26quot%3B%20Congress%20governments%20in%20the%20past%20could%20not%20strengthen%20the%20border%20infrastructure.%20Now%2C%20roads%20and%20modern%20tunnels%20are%20being%20built%20along%20the%20borders%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20questioning%20the%20entity%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20opposing%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20party%20was%20forgiven%20for%20this%20and%20invited%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20but%20it%20chose%20to%20boycott%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoing%20one%20step%20ahead%20it%20has%20now%20publicly%20declared%20a%20war%20against%20Shakti%20in%20Hindu%20religion%20symbolised%20by%20revered%20goddesses%20like%20Maa%20Dhari%20Devi%2C%20Maa%20Chandrabadni%20and%20Jwalpa%20Devi%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20addressing%20the%20BJP's%20Vijay%20Sankalp%20Rally%20at%20the%20IDPL's%20hockey%20ground%20in%20Rishikesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20declaration%20by%20the%20Congress%20will%20add%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire%20in%20the%20ongoing%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B%20to%20destroy%20the%20culture%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20asking%20people%20to%20give%20a%20%26quot%3Bbefitting%20reply%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20opposition%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20referring%20to%20a%20recent%20remark%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20The%20party%20had%20later%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20took%20the%20comment%20out%20of%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20Uttarakhand%20as%20the%20land%20of%20the%20flower%20'Brahma%20kamal'%2C%20he%20asked%20people%20to%20push%20the%20lotus%20button%20during%20polling%20and%20put%20all%20five%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20into%20the%20BJP's%20kitty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20this%20was%20necessary%20to%20fulfil%20its%20pledge%20for%20a%20developed%20India%2C%20of%20which%20a%20developed%20Uttarakhand%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20significant%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20my%20expectations%20are%20even%20bigger%20this%20time.%20You%20have%20to%20break%20all%20past%20records.%20You%20have%20to%20win%20all%20booths%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20confident%20that%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20will%20teach%20the%20Congress%20a%20lesson%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20his%20government%20has%20stopped%20the%20loot%20by%20the%20corrupt%20so%20their%20anger%20against%20him%20is%20at%20its%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsn't%20corruption%20detrimental%20to%20the%20country%3F%20Shouldn't%20the%20country%20get%20rid%20of%20it%3F%20I%20am%20fighting%20this%20big%20war%20with%20the%20strength%20of%20your%20blessings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%20the%20advantages%20of%20government%20schemes%20did%20not%20reach%20the%20beneficiaries%20due%20to%20middlemen%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20under%20the%20BJP%20government%20benefits%20of%20the%20schemes%20are%20reaching%20the%20beneficiaries%20directly%20through%20their%20bank%20accounts%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20the%20past%2C%20the%20country%20has%20been%20strengthened%20manifold%20under%20a%20strong%20and%20stable%20BJP%20government%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20terrorists%20were%20now%20being%20hit%20on%20their%20home%20turf%20-%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eghar%20mein%20ghus%20kar%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20-%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20time%20when%20%26quot%3Bweak%26quot%3B%20governments%20ran%20the%20country.%20The%20apparent%20reference%20was%20to%20cross-border%20strikes%20in%20recent%20years%20after%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20strong%20BJP%20government%20also%20had%20the%20courage