20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20overhead%20view%20of%20passengers%20in%20the%20check-in%20area%20at%20Dublin%20Airport%20Terminal%202%20in%20December%202021.%20Image%20used%20for%20illustration%20purposes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6617b0c61caec1275a6ef279%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPassengers%20at%20Dublin%20Airport%20Terminal%202%20in%20December%202021.%20Image%20for%20illustration%20purposes%20only.%3Cp%3EClodagh%20Kilcoyne%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20airport%20apologized%20for%20asking%20a%20woman%20to%20remove%20her%20prosthetic%20breast%20while%20in%20a%20security%20line.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20passenger%20said%20she%20felt%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Brabbit%20in%20the%20headlights%26quot%3B%20when%20the%20demand%20was%20made.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDublin%20Airport%20said%20private%20screenings%20are%20available%20and%20that%20it's%20working%20to%20ensure%20it%20doesn't%20happen%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDublin%20Airport%20has%20apologized%20after%20a%20passenger%20was%20told%20by%20security%20staff%20to%20remove%20her%20prosthetic%20breast%20in%20public%20as%20she%20passed%20through%20airport%20scanners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERealt%C3%A1n%20N%C3%AD%20Leann%C3%A1in%20told%20BBC%20Radio%20Ulster%20that%20the%20airport's%20body%20scanners%20highlighted%20her%20prosthesis%2C%20the%20result%20of%20a%20mastectomy%2C%20as%20she%20traveled%20from%20the%20Irish%20capital%20to%20Donegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20telling%20airport%20security%20that%20the%20alert%20was%20caused%20by%20her%20prosthesis%2C%20she%20was%20told%20to%20remove%20it%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fprogrammes%2Fm001y39z%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20told%20BBC%20Radio%20Ulster%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20terminal%20was%20crowded%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EN%C3%AD%20Leann%C3%A1in%20said%20she%20was%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Brabbit%20in%20the%20headlights%2C%26quot%3B%20too%20startled%20to%20do%20anything%20but%20comply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20staff's%20attitude%20was%20as%20if%20they'd%20told%20her%20to%20put%20an%20%26quot%3Borange%20jumpsuit%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20even%20the%20physical%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20me%2C%20as%20in%2C%20'I%20need%20to%20see%20it.%20I%20need%20to%20see%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EN%C3%AD%20Leann%C3%A1in%20said%20she%20was%20not%20offered%20a%20private%20space%20to%20remove%20it%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20the%20prosthesis%20half%20out%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20fiddly%20because%20it%20sits%20in%20a%20pocket%20%E2%80%94%20she%20said%20she%20wasn't%20made%20to%20continue%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20when%20the%20woman%2C%20the%20female%20security%20guard%2C%20maybe%20realized%20she%20hadn't%20been%20going%20down%20the%20right%20road%2C%26quot%3B%20N%C3%AD%20Leann%C3%A1in%20told%20BBC%20Radio%20Ulster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDublin%20Airport%20representatives%20later%20apologized%20after%20N%C3%AD%20Leann%C3%A1in%20complained%2C%20she%20said%2C%20but%20wouldn't%20commit%20to%20saying%20it%20wouldn't%20happen%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDublin%20Airport%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20BI's%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20it%20did%20apologize%20to%20N%C3%AD%20Leann%C3%A1in%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BBC%20Radio%20Ulster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20airport%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20it%20had%20investigated%20the%20incident%20and%20agreed%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bshould%20have%20been%20handled%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPassengers%20can%20ask%20for%20a%20private%20screening%20but%20%26quot%3Bregrettably%2C%20this%20did%20not%20happen%20on%20the%20day%20in%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20has%20taken%20steps%20to%20ensure%20similar%20situations%20are%20avoided%20in%20the%20future%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20N%C3%AD%20Leann%C3%A1in%20said%20she's%20concerned%20that%20not%20enough%20people%20are%20aware%20they%20can%20request%20a%20private%20screening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20it's%20not%20just%20people%20with%20prostheses%20who%20might%20be%20affected%2C%20but%20also%20people%20with%20colostomy%20bags%2C%20among%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirport%20security%20lines%2C%20and%20their%20intrusive%20searches%2C%20have%20long%20been%20a%20source%20of%20anger%20and%20frustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20solutions%20could%20eventually%20help%20to%20reduce%20their%20need.%20In%20March%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-self-service-security-screening-airport-test-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarry%20Reid%20International%20Airport%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20trialed%20a%20self-checkout-style%20security%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20said%20may%20help%20to%20reduce%20pat-downs%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-told-remove-prosthetic-breast-in-crowded-airport-security-dublin-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712833494000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6617b43f3f923f7dab06af55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-told-remove-prosthetic-breast-in-crowded-airport-security-dublin-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dublin%20Airport%20apologized%20after%20a%20passenger%20was%20told%20by%20security%20to%20remove%20her%20prosthetic%20breast%20in%20public%20as%20she%20passed%20through%20airport%20scanners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mia%20Jankowicz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-told-remove-prost