ess-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-passenger-electric-shell-india-partner-for-ev-charging-stations-124041100438_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shell%20India%20Markets%20Director%20Sanjay%20Varkey%20said%20the%20company%20is%20committed%20to%20define%20the%20EV%20charging%20experience%20by%20offering%20integrated%20solutions%20that%20prioritise%20convenience%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20sustainability%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-passenger-electric-shell-india-partner-for-ev-charging-stations-124041100438_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-passenger-electric-shell-india-partner-for-ev-charging-stations-124041100438_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-passenger-electric-shell-india-partner-for-ev-charging-stations-124041100438_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World's%20Largest%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%20Now%20In%20India%20-%205%20Times%20Paris's%20Size%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20narrow%20airstrip%20that%20doesn't%20even%20have%20an%20air%20traffic%20controller%20to%20guide%20incoming%20airplanes%20and%20whose%20only%20infrastructure%20is%20a%20portable%20toilet%20and%20a%20make-shift%20office%20in%20a%20container%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20miles%20of%20barren%20land%20bordering%20Pakistan%20is%20an%20unlikely%20gateway%20to%20the%20world's%20largest%20renewable%20energy%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airstrip%20was%20even%20smaller%20in%20December%202022%2C%20when%20Adani%20group%20head%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20who%20was%20then%20the%20second%20richest%20person%20in%20the%20world%2C%20first%20used%20a%20small%20aircraft%20to%20reach%20the%20barren%20area%20that%20didn't%20even%20have%20a%20pincode%20and%20got%20its%20name%20from%20a%20village%2080-kilometers%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20hardly%20had%20any%20vegetation%20due%20to%20its%20highly%20saline%20soil%2C%20leave%20alone%20any%20habitation.%20But%20the%20area%20with%20second%20best%20solar%20radiation%20in%20the%20country%20after%20Ladakh%20and%20wind%20speeds%20five%20times%20of%20plains%2C%20served%20as%20an%20idle%20location%20for%20a%20renewable%20energy%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%2018-km%20drive%20from%20the%20airstrip%20through%20dusty%20arid%20land%20is%20the%20site%20for%20his%20group's%20Khavda%20renewable%20energy%20park%20spread%20over%20538%20square%20kilometers%20-%20roughly%20five%20times%20the%20size%20of%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Adani%20first%20landed%20at%20Khavda%2C%20he%20joked%20if%20anyone%20could%20even%20find%20a%20mosquito%20in%20the%20area%2C%20his%20executives%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20then%2C%20his%20group%20has%20not%20just%20laid%20solar%20panels%20that%20will%20convert%20sun%20rays%20into%20electricity%20and%20wind%20mills%20to%20harness%20wind%20blowing%20at%20the%20speed%20of%208%20meters%20per%20second%2C%20but%20also%20built%20colonies%20for%20workers%2C%20put%20up%20desalination%20plants%20to%20make%20saline%20water%20pumped%20out%20of%20700%20meters%20below%20ground%20portable%20and%20utilities%20such%20as%20mobile%20phone%20repair%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Green%20Energy%20Ltd%2C%20India's%20largest%20renewable%20energy%20company%2C%20will%20invest%20about%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20crore%20to%20generate%2030%20megawatts%20of%20clean%20electricity%20at%20Khavda%20in%20Gujarat's%20Kutch%2C%20it's%20Managing%20Director%20Vneet%20Jaain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20just%20now%20commissioned%202%2C000%20MW%20(2%20GW)%20of%20capacity%20at%20Khavda%20and%20plan%20to%20add%204%20GW%20in%20the%20current%20fiscal%20(financial%20year%20ending%20March%202025)%20and%205%20GW%20every%20year%20thereafter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airstrip%20is%20used%20to%20ferry%20group%20executives%20from%20Mundra%20or%20Ahmedabad%20a%20few%20times%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20traffic%20controller%20or%20ATC%20at%20Bhuj%2C%20some%20160-km%20away%2C%20is%20the%20last%20guide%20post%20for%20airplanes%20going%20to%20Khavda.%20But%20it's%20reach%20is%20only%20till%20'Tent%20City'%20and%20pilots%20are%20virtually%20on%20their%20own%20for%20the%20last%20leg%20of%2080-km%20or%20so%20including%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20use%20visual%20aids%20and%20airplanes'%20navigation%20systems%20to%20land.%20When%20taking%20off%2C%20we%20convey%20to%20Bhuj%20about%20the%20plans%20over%20phone%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20pilot%20flying%20the%20Adani%20Group-owned%20plane%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outer%20flange%20of%20the%20energy%20park%20is%20just%20one%20km%20from%20the%20international%20border%20with%20Pakistan.%20The%20one-km%20buffer%20is%20manned%20by%20BSF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExecutives%20said%20the%20airstrip%20was%20built%20in%20just%2035%20days%20in%20an%20area%20where%20even%20tractors%20had%20to%20be%20modified%20so%20they%20could%20operate%20in%20land%20that%20doesn't%20easily%20absorb%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20has%20its%20own%20set%20of%20challenges%20-%20heavy%20dust%20storms%20during%20March%20to%20June%2C%20no%20communication%20and%20transport%20infrastructure%2C%20nearest%20habitable%20area%20being%2080-km%20away%2C%20water%20not%20seeping%20under%20soil%20during%20rainy%20season%2C%20even%20ground%20water%20being%20saline%20and%20it%20being%20a%20restricted%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExecutives%20said%20while%20some%20workers%20from%20Khavda%20village%2C%20accommodation%20are%20being%20built%20to%20house%208%2C000%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20group's%20renewable%20energy%20plans%20are%20the%20most%20ambitious%20by%20any%20corporate%20in%20the%20country%20which%20is%20targeting%20to%20generate%20500%20GW%20of%20electricity%20from%20non-fossil%20sources%20by%202030%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20plan%20of%20achieving%20net-zero%20emissions%20by%202070.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhavda%20at%20its%20peak%20will%20generate%2081%20billion%20units%20that%20can%20power%20entire%20nations%20such%20as%20Belgium%2C%20Chile%20and%20Switzerland%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaain%20said%20the%2030%20GW%20planned%20at%20Khavda%20would%20comprise%2026%20GW%20of%20solar%20and%204%20GW%20of%20wind%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAGEL's%20existing%20operational%20portfolio%20comprises%207%2C393%20MW%20solar%2C%201%2C401%20MW%20wind%20and%202%2C140%20MW%20wind-solar%20hybrid%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Khavda%20region%20witnesses%202%2C060%20kWh%2Fm2%20of%20high%20solar%20irradiation%20and%20one%20of%20the%20best%20wind%20resources%20in%20India%2C%20with%20speeds%20of%208%20meters%20per%20second%2C%20frequent%20sandstorms%20necessitate%20cleaning%20of%20solar%20panels%20several%20times%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProject%20will%20be%20entirely%20covered%20with%20waterless%20robotic%20module%20cleaning%20systems%2C%20executives%20said.%20Khavda%20land%20belongs%20to%20the%20government%2C%20which%20leased%20out%20the%20site%20to%20Adani%20group%20for%2040%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExecutives%20said%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20Adani%20Green%20conducted%20geotechnical%20investigations%2C%20seismic%20studies%2C%20a%20centrifuge%20study%20by%20Cambridge%2C%20resource%20assessment%20and%20land%20studies%2C%20Environment%20and%20Social%20Impact%20Assessment%20(ESIA)%2C%20Environmental%20and%20Social%20Due%20Diligence%20(ESDD)%2C%20and%20a%20detailed%20feasibility%20study%2C%20amongst%20several%20others%2C%20before%20embarking%20on%20the%20development%20of%20this%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstruction%20started%20in%202022.%20The%20comprehensive%20infrastructure%20development%20effort%20included%20the%20construction%20of%20100%20km%20roads%2C%2050%20km%20of%20drainage%2C%20establishment%20of%20desalination%20and%203%20reverse%20osmosis%20(RO)%20plants%20with%20a%20total%20capacity%20of%2070%20cubic%20meter%20per%20hour%20to%20meet%20the%20drinking%20water%20requirements%20of%20the%20project%20staff%2C%20laying%20optical%20fiber%20cables%20for%20180%20km%20for%20connectivity%2C%20and%20concrete%20batching%20plants.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712832840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fo56gq6mk_khavda-worlds-largest-renewable-energy-park_625x300_11_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworlds-largest-renewable-energy-park-now-in-india-5-times-larger-than-paris-5419130%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20narrow%20airstrip%20that%20doesn't%20even%20have%20an%20air%20traffic%20controller%20to%20guide%20incoming%20planes%20and%20whose%20only%20infrastructure%20is%20a%20portable%20toilet%20and%20a%20make-shift%20office%20in%20a%20container%20is%20an%20unlikely%20gateway%20to%20the%20world's%20largest%20renewable%20energy%20park.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworlds-largest-renewable-energy-park-now-in-india-5-times-larger-than-paris-5419130%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworlds-largest-renewable-energy-park-now-in-india-5-times-larger-than-paris-5419130%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworlds-largest-renewable-energy-park-now-in-india-5-times-larger-than-paris-5419130%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%