ife%20there%3F%26quot%3B%20Sanjana%2C%20the%20fast%20bowler's%20wife%2C%20asked%20Bumrah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20had%20these%20conversations%20before.%20Every%20boy%20wants%20to%20make%20it%20big%20and%20play%20cricket.%20Every%20street%20has%2025%20players%20who%20want%20to%20play%20for%20India.%20You%20have%20to%20have%20a%20backup%20plan.%20Our%20relative%20lives%20there.%20I%20though%20I%20will%20finish%20my%20education%20and...my%20uncle%20lives%20there.%20First%20we%20though%20we%20would%20go%20as%20a%20family%2C%20then%20my%20mum%20did%20not%20want%20to%20go%20there%20as%20it's%20a%20different%20culture.%20I%20am%20very%20happy%20and%20very%20lucky%20that%20things%20worked%20out%2C%20Otherwise%20I%20don't%20know%20I%20would%20have%20tried%20to%20play%20for%20the%20Canadian%20team%20and%20do%20something%20there%20as%20well.%20Glad%20it%20worked%20out%20here.%20I%20am%20playing%20for%20the%20Indian%20team%20and%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%26quot%3B%20Bumrah%20told%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiocinema.com%2Fsports%2Fthe-bumrah-interview-with-sanjana-ganesan%2F3948065%3Faf_force_deeplink%3Dtrue%26source_caller%3Dapi%26pid%3Dmobile_share%26shortlink%3Dic5jsdc5%26af_adset%3DShare%2520CAC%2520Adset%26af_ad%3DShare%2520for%2520The%2520Bumrah%2520Interview%2520With%2520Sanjana%2520Ganesan%26deep_link_value%3Djiovootviacom18%253A%252F%252Fjiovoot%252Fplayback%252F3948065%26af_channel%3DShare%2520Button%26c%3DShare%2520Media%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJio%20Cinema%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20former%20Indian%20cricket%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Manoj%20Tiwary%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F916-manoj-tiwary-playerprofile%5C%22%3EManoj%20Tiwary%3C%2Fa%3E%20commented%20that%20he%20would%20want%20Bumrah%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Shami%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1580-shami-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Shami%3