2C%26quot%3B%20Muller%20told%20me.%20As%20they're%20rethinking%20what's%20worth%20their%20investment%2C%20many%20are%20prioritizing%20what's%20right%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20investing%20into%20my%20apartment%2C%26quot%3B%20Muller%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20investing%20into%20my%20happiness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20avocado-toast%20generation%20has%20often%20been%20derided%20as%20too%20frivolous%20to%20save%20for%20practical%20purchases.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-house-home-real-estate-mortgage-rates-rent-debt-boomers-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillennials'%20housing%20misfortunes%3C%2Fa%3E%20go%20beyond%20personal%20spending%20habits%3B%20they%20entered%20adulthood%20at%20a%20terrible%20time%20for%20the%20housing%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20a%20pretty%20dramatic%20shortfall%20in%20construction%20of%20new%20homes%20going%20back%20now%20like%20a%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jim%20Parrott%2C%20a%20nonresident%20fellow%20at%20the%20Urban%20Institute%20who%20owns%20Parrott%20Ryan%20Advisors.%20He%20said%20the%20pandemic%20only%20exacerbated%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-ice-age-higher-home-prices-fewer-sales-inventory-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20supply%20of%20new%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leading%20to%20increases%20in%20demand%20and%20prices.%20That%20lack%20of%20supply%20has%20especially%20affected%20Black%20Americans%2C%20who%20purchase%20homes%20at%20significantly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nar.realtor%2Fnewsroom%2Fracial-minority-groups-increased-their-homeownership-rates-while-still-facing-significant-homebuying-challenges%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20their%20white%20counterparts.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20putting%20the%20bottom%20rung%20of%20homeownership%20further%20and%20further%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20renters%2C%20it%20disproportionately%20affects%20those%20groups%20relative%20to%20everybody%20else%2C%20because%20more%20of%20them%20are%20renters%2C%26quot%3B%20Parrott%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20interest%20rate%20on%20a%2030-year%20mortgage%20is%20roughly%207%25.%20But%20rather%20than%20lowering%20prices%20and%20demand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomy-housing-market-mortgage-buying-car-interest-rates-new-jobs-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20interest%20rates%20have%20locked%20many%20homeowners%20into%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20preventing%20entry-level%20homeowners%20from%20upgrading%20and%20making%20those%20units%20available%20to%20first-time%20buyers.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what's%20totally%20screwed%20over%20millennials%20as%20folks%20who%20in%20a%20normal%20era%20would%20be%20positioned%20to%20buy%20their%20first%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Parrott%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20pushing%20their%20timeline%20back%20because%20they've%20got%20to%20save%20even%20more%20money%20than%20they%20would%20have%2020%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20how%20Caroline%20Winkler%20felt%20in%202020%20when%20she%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20at%20the%20time%20considered%20buying%20a%20home%20in%20Cincinnati.%20%26quot%3BIt%20became%20instantly%20so%20clear%20that%20that%20would%20be%20years%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20The%20hopelessness%20of%20the%20market%20caused%20her%20to%20give%20up%20on%20her%20homeownership%20dream%2C%20but%20she%20became%20all%20the%20more%20determined%20to%20improve%20her%20situation.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there's%20a%20life%20I%20want%20to%20have%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20make%20it%20possible%20in%20other%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20relocating%20to%20a%20rental%20apartment%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20in%202021%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20her%20family%2C%20Winkler%2C%20now%2032%2C%20has%20built%20a%20YouTube%20audience%20of%20half%20a%20million%20subscribers%20by%20posting%20content%20such%20as%20dating%20stories%20and%20renter-friendly%20home%20updates%20(one%20project%20involved%20installing%20peel-and-stick%20floor%20tiles%20and%20wallpaper%20in%20her%20bathroom).%20Creating%20YouTube%20videos%20allowed%20Winkler%2C%20an%20actor%20turned%20tech%20worker%2C%20to%20explore%20interior%20design%20as%20a%20creative%20outlet%20without%20having%20more-traditional%20certifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20channel%20is%20one%20of%20many%20in%20the%20growing%20rental-reno%20space.%20Others%20include%20Alexandra%20Gater%2C%20a%20YouTuber%20in%20Toronto%20with%20over%20700%2C000%20subscribers%20who%20posts%20videos%20of%20home%20makeovers%20largely%20tailored%20to%20small%20rental%20apartments.%20Her%20team%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20build%20a%20wooden%20arch%20for%20a%20kitchen%20entryway%20in%20a%20rental.%20The%20DIY%20duo%20The%20Sorry%20Girls%20have%20amassed%20more%20than%202%20million%20subscribers%20by%20posting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjCYsivwQsTw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoften%20extreme%3C%2Fa%3E%20renovations%2C%20like%20installing%20a%20custom%20Plexiglass%20room%20divider%20for%20a%20rental%20studio%20apartment.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F28%2Frealestate%2Frenters-upper-west-side.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHattie%20Kolp%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20made%20a%20career%20as%20a%20full-time%20content%20creator%20documenting%20her%20updates%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20adding%20crown%20molding%20%E2%80%94%20to%20her%20family's%20rent-stabilized%20Upper%20West%20Side%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20booming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-tiktok-inspired-24000-tulsa-home-renovation-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial-media%20appetite%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20rental-renovation%20content%20reflects%20not%20only%20the%20tastes%20of%20a%20generation%20raised%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-makeover-shows-ranked-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome-makeover%20TV%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20renovation%20guidance%20among%20renters%20who%20can't%20afford%20a%20home%20%E2%80%94%20or%20professional%20renovation%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%20the%20housing%20market%20was%20soaring%20out%20of%20control%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20people%20were%20spending%20more%20time%20at%20home.%20With%20growing%20savings%20accounts%20and%20stimulus%20checks%2C%20people%20suddenly%20had%20the%20time%2C%20money%2C%20and%20energy%20to%20improve%20their%20living%20space.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-improvement-boom-housing-market-recovery-millennials-pandemic-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHome%20renovations%20exploded%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Benjamin%20Fix%2C%20a%20longtime%20plumber%2C%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20among%20millennial%20renters.%20%26quot%3BMany%20of%20them%20rent%20in%20cities%20like%20New%20York%20or%20San%20Francisco%20or%20wherever.%20And%20they%20in%20fact%20have%20a%20pretty%20high%20disposable%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20Fix%20said.%20In%202022%2C%20he%20launched%20Sproos%2C%20which%20makes%20a%20colorful%2C%20easy-to-install%20showerhead%2C%20marketed%20to%20renters%20who%20were%20spending%20more%20time%20%E2%80%94%20and%20money%20%E2%80%94%20at%20home.%20The%20brand%20quickly%20found%20a%20market%2C%20getting%20picked%20up%20by%20Urban%20Outfitters%20and%20the%20trendy%20New%20York%20home-decor%20boutique%20Coming%20Soon%20within%20a%20year%20of%20launching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Denver%2C%20Rose%20Matthes%20and%20her%20now-wife%20identified%20a%20similar%20opportunity.%20They%20wanted%20to%20install%20bedroom%20lighting%20in%20their%20older%20rental%20home%20in%20the%20city's%20Santa%20Fe%20arts%20district%20in%202020.%20Seeing%20few%20options%20outside%20labor-intensive%20electrical%20work%20or%20cheap%20tap%20lights%2C%20the%20two%20launched%20a%20Kickstarter%20in%202023%20for%20Poplight%2C%20a%20chargeable%20wall%20sconce%20affixed%20with%20Command%20strips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ran%20some%20test%20Facebook%20ads%20to%20see%20if%20I%20can%20get%20people%20to%20submit%20their%20email%20and%20join%20a%20waitlist%20for%20a%20product%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthes%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20built%20an%20email%20list%20of%20almost%2010%2C000%20people%20in%20two%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20wife%20rely%20heavily%20on%20social%20media%20for%20their%20home%20inspiration.%20%26quot%3BI%20start%20every%20home-improvement%20project%20by%20watching%20someone%20do%20that%20project%20on%20YouTube%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthes%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20obsession%20on%20aesthetics%20is%20driven%20by%20social%20media%2C%20because%20I%20think%20you%20see%20people%20doing%20things%20that%20you%20didn't%20know%20you%20could%20do%20for%20under%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinkler%2C%20the%20creator%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20social%20media%20doesn't%20always%20reflect%20reality.%20%26quot%3BThe%20bathroom%20makeover%20that%20I%20did%20in%20my%20own%20apartment%2C%20I%20basically%20wouldn't%20have%20done%20that%20makeover%20if%20I%20didn't%20make%20a%20living%20off%20of%20sharing%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20something%20to%20the%20internet%20I%20think%20affecting%20the%20standard%20that%20people%20expect%20for%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20that%20standard%20is%20positive.%20Zamora%2C%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20content%20creator%2C%20said%20that%20one%20of%20his%20followers%20messaged%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20make%20me%20want%20to%20make%20my%20home%20feel%20like%20a%20home%20no%20matter%20how%20temporary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20River%20Nice%2C%20a%20financial%20planner%20in%20the%20Philadelphia%20area%2C%20emphasized%20that%20buying%20is%20a%20better%20long-term%20financial%20investment%20than%20renting%20for%20people%20who%20have%20the%20means%2C%20they%20said%20a%20stable%20living%20situation%20comes%20down%20to%20more%20than%20money.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20fault%20anybody%20who%20is%20like%2C%20the%20only%20chance%20that%20they%20get%20to%20live%20in%20New%20York%20or%20San%20Francisco%20is%20to%20rent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nice%2C%20who%20owns%20the%20financial-planning%20firm%20Be%20Intentional%20Financial.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20they%20have%20better%20job%20opportunities%2C%20or%20maybe%20they%20have%20more%20safety%20for%20their%20identities%20in%20those%20locations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20they've%20been%20locked%20out%20of%20the%20housing%20market%20or%20they%20live%20in%20an%20expensive%20city%2C%20buying%20a%20home%20is%20simply%20not%20in%20the%20cards%20for%20many%20people.%20And%20these%20long-term%20renters%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20the%20best%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20an%20ideal%20world%20it%20would%20absolutely%20be%20the%20case%20that%20renters%20shouldn't%20have%20to%20invest%20their%20own%20time%20and%20money%20into%20their%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mercury%20Stardust%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BSafe%20and%20Sound%3A%20A%20Renter-Friendly%20Guide%20to%20Home%20Repair%26quot%3B%20who%20shares%20renter-friendly%20repair%20tips%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40mercurystardust%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20Trans%20Handy%20Ma'am.%20%26quot%3BSo%20many%20of%20us%20put%20money%20into%20our%20rentals%20because%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20it%20feel%20like%20the%20warm%2C%20inviting%20space%20that%20we%20need%20in%20our%20life.%20I%20think%20that%20should%20be%20a%20universal%20truth%20rather%20than%20something%20that%20only%20homeowners%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20now%20a%20growing%20select%20few%20%E2%80%94%