20the%20line.%20It%20stretched%20back%2050%20feet%20from%20the%20actual%20entrance%2C%20which%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20series%20of%20winding%20metal%20gates%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20TSA%20checkpoint.%20Directly%20in%20front%20of%20the%20entrance%2C%20there%20was%20a%20sea%20of%20people%20going%20shoulder%20to%20shoulder%2C%20trudging%20along%2C%20trying%20to%20make%20their%20way%20to%20the%20actual%20course.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20going%20between%20stages%20at%20a%20music%20festival.%20I%20would've%20snapped%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20hubbub%2C%20but%20the%20Masters'%20no-phone%20rule%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20document%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20in%20the%20main%20line%20is%20more%20like%20waiting%20for%20a%20ride%20at%20Disney%20than%20anything.%20Once%20you%20enter%20the%20building%20structure%2C%20there's%20another%20huge%20room%20and%20corridor%20with%20gates%20snaking%20around.%20At%20every%20turn%20the%20line%20seems%20to%20extend.%20What's%20another%2020%20minutes%20when%20that%20sweet%20merch%20is%20within%20grasp%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%2045%20minutes%20all%20in%2C%20we%20made%20it%20to%20the%20actual%20shop.%20The%20final%20step%20is%20to%20wait%20for%20roughly%20five%20minutes%20in%20an%20entryway%20before%20they%20let%20in%20a%20new%20flood%20of%20shoppers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you're%20inside%2C%20the%20mania%20is%20overwhelming.%20There%20are%20separate%20alcoved%20sections%20for%20men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20kids.%20In%20the%20center%20of%20the%20space%20is%20a%20giant%20houseware%20display.%20Countless%20shirts%20and%20hats%20are%20displayed%20and%20numbered%20high%20on%20a%20wall%2C%20and%20busy%20workers%20rush%20to%20fetch%20items%20from%20bins%20stacked%20high%20with%20various%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20checkout%20lines%2C%20each%20with%20at%20least%20five%20registers%20on%20either%20side.%20The%20cashiers%20crank%20through%20piles%20of%20merch%2C%20run%20credit%20cards%2C%20and%20move%20on%20to%20the%20next.%20It's%20an%20impressive%20assembly%20line%20of%20capitalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20purchasing%20a%20polo%20shirt%2C%20a%20T-shirt%2C%20a%20hat%2C%20and%20a%20cup.%20Compared%20to%20almost%20everyone%20else%20around%20me%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20meager%20haul%2C%20and%20I%20wound%20up%20toting%20around%20a%20single%20bag%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22masters%202024%20golf%20shop%20exterior%20crowd%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6616ceab16bde8d4ead763f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20sea%20of%20people%20near%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20Masters%20golf%20shop%2C%20on%20April%209%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EBen%20Jared%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20experience%20left%20me%20feeling%20like%20the%20Masters%20has%20become%20a%20retail%20juggernaut%20that%20just%20so%20happens%20to%20put%20on%20a%20golf%20tournament.%20And%20the%20numbers%20bear%20that%20out.%20According%20to%20a%20Forbes%20study%20of%20the%202022%20Masters%2C%20the%20tournament%20raked%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fjustinteitelbaum%2F2022%2F04%2F07%2Fthe-masters-tournament-at-augusta-is-leaving-269-million-on-the-putting-green%2F%3Fsh%3D7a39bc065eb1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2469%20million%20of%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20merch%2C%20far%20more%20than%20it%20made%20from%20tickets%20and%20concessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20attendance%20figures%20aren't%20public%2C%20if%20you%20go%20off%20the%2040%2C000-per-day%20estimate%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20consensus%2C%20that%20comes%20out%20to%20about%20%24246%20a%20person%20spent%20at%20the%20merch%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20assumes%20endless%20supply.%20According%20to%20a%20guy%20I%20met%20at%20my%20hotel%2C%20the%20prior%20year%20they'd%20stopped%20sales%20by%20Friday%20due%20to%20depleted%20inventory.%20It's%20also%20possible%20people%20are%20less%20merch-obsessed%20from%20Thursday%20to%20Sunday%20when%20the%20actual%20tournament%20is%20going%20on.%20So%20it's%20the%20Monday-through-Wednesday%20practice-round%20crowd%20driving%20up%20that%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20likely%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20typical%20patron%20is%20ponying%20up%20even%20more%20than%20that%20%24246.%20And%20the%20people%20with%20the%20six%20bags%20were%20surely%20toting%20five%20figures%20worth%20of%20swag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20in%20the%20end%2C%20what's%20it%20all%20for%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20pretty%20straightforward%3A%20street%20cred%20and%20status.%20Golf%20is%20already%20an%20expensive%20sport%20largely%20played%20by%20the%20affluent.%20For%20one%20to%20stand%20out%20in%20that%20already-elite%20crowd%2C%20extreme%20measures%20must%20be%20taken.%20Lines%20must%20be%20waited%20in%2C%20and%20hundreds%20(thousands%3F)%20must%20be%20shelled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20if%20you'll%20excuse%20me%2C%20I%20need%20to%20head%20to%20the%20store%20wearing%20my%20new%20Masters%20hat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-2024-merchandise-sale-store-shopping-golf-accessories-garden-gnome-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712828102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6616b7381caec1275a6e8cb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-2024-merchandise-sale-store-shopping-golf-accessories-garden-gnome-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you%20went%20to%20the%20Masters%20and%20didn't%20buy%20a%20mountain%20of%20swag%20to%20show%20off%2C%20did%20you%20truly%20go%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jciolli%40businessinsider.com%20(Joe%20Ciolli)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmasters-2024-merchandise-sale-store-shopping-golf-accessories-garde