80%99%20livestock.%20And%20Namgail%20emphasises%20that%20this%20is%20where%20the%20conservancy%20steps%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20alongside%20the%20ferocious%20predator%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20dream%20for%20the%20pastoral%20communities%20of%20Ladakh.%20However%2C%20being%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F96401%2Fproject-shen-snow-leopard-conservation-women-handicrafts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaintain%20their%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20money%20they%20earn%20through%20protecting%20it%20serves%20as%20an%20incentive.%20In%20fact%2C%20once%20hailed%20as%20pests%2C%20Namgail%20says%20the%20felines%20are%20now%20fondly%20called%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERi%20Gyancha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98ornaments%20of%20the%20mountains%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20this%20nickname%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20soften%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20snow%20leopard%20towards%20the%20locals%20who%20continue%20to%20see%20rare%20cases%20of%20their%20cattle%20being%20mauled%20and%20eaten.%20But%20at%20least%20now%2C%20they%20are%20reimbursed%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENamgail%20notes%20that%20the%20insurance%20model%20is%20only%20one%20of%20the%20many%20activities%20at%20the%20conservancy.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20focus%20on%20community-based%20tourism%2C%20education%20and%20research%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20and%20promotion%20of%20innovative%20grass-root%20measures%20that%20encourage%20local%20people%20to%20become%20better%20stewards%20of%20the%20endangered%20snow%20leopards%2C%20their%20prey%2C%20and%20habitats.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20arm%20of%20the%20conservancy%20is%20the%20award-winning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334115%2Fbest-homestays-in-himachal-pradesh-uttarakhand-to-enjoy-snowfall-in-winter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHimalayan%20Homestay%