ial-intelligence%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20(AI)%20editing%20tools%20on%20its%20Google%20Photos%20app%20available%20to%20all%20Android%20and%20iOS%20users%20on%20Wednesday.%20This%20includes%20the%20Magic%20Eraser%2C%20Photo%20Unblur%2C%20and%20Portrait%20light%20features%20introduced%20with%20the%20Pixel%207%20series.%20Additionally%2C%20non-Pixel%20users%20will%20also%20get%20limited%20usage%20of%20the%20Magic%20Editor%20tool%20which%20was%20launched%20with%20the%20Pixel%208%20series.%20Notably%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20has%20made%20several%20major%20announcements%20this%20week%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fai%2Fnews%2Fgoogle-workspace-update-vids-app-generative-ai-features-added-5411884%5C%22%3Eadding%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20new%20app%20to%20Workspace%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Fai%2Fnews%2Fgoogle-gemini-pro-1-5-ai-model-public-preview-new-features-5413614%5C%22%3Ebringing%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gemini%201.5%20Pro%20to%20public%20preview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fproducts%2Fphotos%2Fgoogle-photos-editing-features-availability%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannouncement%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20made%20by%20Dina%20Berrada%2C%20Director%20of%20Product%20Management%2C%20Google%20Photos%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CStarting%20on%20May%2015%2C%20many%20of%20our%20AI-powered%20editing%20tools%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Magic%20Eraser%2C%20Photo%20Unblur%20and%20Portrait%20light%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20available%20to%20anyone%20using%20Google%20Photos%2C%20no%20subscription%20required.%20You'll%20also%20be%20able%20to%20access%20these%20features%20on%20more%20devices%2C%20including%20Pixel%20tablets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Magic%20Eraser%20feature%20is%20similar%20to%20Oppo's%20AI%20Erase%20and%20Samsung's%20Object%20Eraser.%20When%20a%20user%20circles%20a%20background%20object%20in%20a%20photo%2C%20the%20AI%20automatically%20removes%20it%2C%20while%20restoring%20the%20background%20elements.%20Photo%20Unblur%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Ftags%2Fgoogle%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20uses%20machine%20learning%20and%20facial%20recognition%20to%20sharpen%20blurred%20images%20and%20clarify%20facial%20features.%20Portrait%20light%20can%20change%20the%20position%20of%20the%20source%20of%20light%20in%20an%20image%20with%20fewer%20than%20four%20people.%20Users%20can%20also%20change%20the%20intensity%20of%20light%20using%20a%20slider.%20All%20these%20three%20features%20will%20be%20available%20to%20all%20Android%20and%20iOS%20users%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20AI%20editing%20tool%20that%20is%20being%20expanded%20is%20the%20Magic%20Editor.%20It%20uses%20generative%20AI%20to%20make%20complex%20photo%20edits%20with%20simple%20gesture-based%20actions.%20It%20can%20perform%20tasks%20such%20as%20repositioning%20an%20object%2C%20changing%20the%20background%2C%20and%20more.%20The%20feature%20is%20currently%20available%20only%20in%20the%20Pixel%208%20series%2C%20but%20after%20May%2015%2C%20it%20will%20be%20available%20in%20all%20Pixel%20smartphones.%20Additionally%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Ftags%2Fandroid%5C%22%3EAndroid%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Ftags%2Fios%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20users%20will%20get%20to%20make%20up%20to%2010%20edits%20a%20month%20using%20the%20feature.%20To%20use%20the%20feature%20beyond%20this%2C%20users%20will%20need%20to%20subscribe%20to%20the%20Premium%20Google%20One%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20features%20will%20be%20made%20available%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Ftags%2Fgoogle-photos%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Photos%3C%2Fa%3E%20users%20on%20May%2015%2C%20which%20is%20a%20day%20after%20Google%20I%2FO%202024%2C%20the%20company's%20annual%20developer-focused%20event.%20It%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20tech%20giant%20will%20unveil%20Android%2015%20during%20the%20event%2C%20which%20might%20introduce%20new%20AI%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fo9jRrIRzuVE%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cem%3EIs%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%205%20the%20best%20foldable%20phone%20you%20can%20buy%20in%20India%20right%20now%3F%20We%20discuss%20the%20company's%20new%20clamshell-style%20foldable%20handset%20on%20the%20latest%20episode%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gadgets360.com%2Ftags%2Forbital%5C%22%3EOrbital%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Gadgets%20360%20podcast.%20Orbital%20is%20available%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fshow%2F1TQIHsTESxrsHleJVhUKcr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpotify%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgaana.com%2Fpodcast%2Forbital-season-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGaana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiosaavn.com%2Fshows%2Forbital%2F1%2Fr9VmNAJ211U%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJioSaavn%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.google.com%2Ffeed%2FaHR0cHM6Ly9jZG4uZ2FkZ2V0czM2MC5jb20vY29udGVudC9kYXRhL3htbC9vcmJpdGFsLnhtbA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Podcasts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fin%2Fpodcast%2Forbital-gadgets-360-podcast%2Fid1121036073%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Podcasts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmusic.amazon.in%2Fpodcasts%2Fe3a8ca64-3005-4427-a89e-b3e8ec828c3b%2FOrbital%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Music%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20wherever%20you%20get%20your%20podcasts.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%