20to%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295229%2Ftaj-icecream-mumbai-eatery-loved-by-madhubala-makes-natural-icecream-in-wooden-barrels%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20draw%20for%20celebrities%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Ambanis%2C%20the%20Birlas%2C%20and%20the%20Tatas%2C%20they%20must%20be%20doing%20something%20right!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20anyone%20will%20affirm%2C%20a%20menu%20boasting%20scrumptious%20sweets%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20draw%20of%20this%20dairy%20venture%20located%20off%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Princess%20Street.%20It%20is%20its%20century-old%20charm%20and%20the%20recipe%20that%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20generations%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20where%20the%20magic%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20wondering%20why%20the%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20has%20continued%20to%20see%20an%20unwavering%20customer%20base%20for%20over%20108%20years%20now%2C%20the%20proof%20is%20literally%20and%20metaphorically%20in%20the%20pudding.%20The%20history%20of%20the%20business%20ties%20back%20to%20when%20a%20young%20boy%20of%2016%20began%20delivering%20milk%20cans%20to%20homes%20around%20Kalbadevi%20(an%20old%20neighbourhood%20in%20Mumbai).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20Nariman%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20first%20choice%20of%20a%20job.%20Circumstances%20led%20him%20to%20it%2C%20and%20ambition%20paved%20the%20way%20to%20success.%20Since%201916%2C%20when%20Ardeshir%20sold%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327249%2Fkota-engineer-runs-sustainable-dairy-farm-saves-on-electricy-bills-gau-organics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20can%20of%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20seen%20its%20trajectory%20of%20ups%20interspersed%20with%20downs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20fourth%20generation%20settles%20down%20to%20chat%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20they%20say%20challenges%20are%20a%20part%20of%20any%20business.%20What%20sets%20the%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20apart%2C%20however%2C%20is%20its%20recipe%20for%20dealing%20with%20adversity.%20The%20women%20and%20children%20have%20never%20shied%20away%20from%20steering%20the%20legacy%20forward%20when%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20cousins%20laugh%20over%20childhood%20anecdotes%2C%20stories%20of%20taking%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20family%20legacy%20and%20nostalgic%20memories%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20clear%20%E2%80%94%20the%20dairy%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20just%20a%20family%20business%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20loved%20member%20that%20has%20had%20its%20own%20seat%20at%20the%20family%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChildhood%20summers%20and%20hot%20piping%20%3Cem%3Ejalebis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20family%20behind%20the%20legacy%20of%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345654%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20family%20behind%20the%