0the%20future%20generations%20but%20changing%20the%20concept%20of%20employment.%20The%20report%20also%20indicates%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345161%2Ftvaran-by-cisco-villgro-empower-women-led-startups-female-entrepreneurs-climate-action%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estartup%20ecosystem%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20will%20create%20over%2010%20lakh%20jobs%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20Indian%20School%20of%20Business%20(ISB)%2C%20through%20their%20one-of-a-kind%20%E2%80%98I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20programme%20is%20providing%20the%20required%20support%20to%20this%20ecosystem%20and%20championing%20entrepreneurship%20for%20every%20section%20of%20the%20society%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20its%20purview%2C%20there%20are%20various%20programmes%20all%20fostering%20entrepreneurship%20and%20nurturing%20startups%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20%E2%80%98Start-to-Scale%E2%80%99%20support%20that%20will%20accelerate%20their%20conversion%20into%20profitable%20ventures.%20One%20such%20recently%20launched%20programme%20%E2%80%98DiscoverShe%E2%80%99%2C%20brings%20together%20the%20goals%20of%20a%20profitable%20venture%20while%20upholding%20the%20inclusion%20of%20women%20in%20business%20by%20empowering%20women%20micro-entrepreneurs%20to%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20series%20of%20%3Cem%3Eyatras%3C%2Fem%3E%20(roadshows)%20in%20Tier%202%20and%203%20cities%20of%20India%2C%20DiscoverShe%20is%20set%20to%20provide%20a%20platform%20for%20these%20women%20entrepreneurs%20to%20pitch%20their%20ideas%20and%20engage%20with%20investors%2C%20mentors%20and%20other%20stakeholders.%20But%20as%20Saumya%20Kumar%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%20highlights%2C%20a%20significant%20obstacle%20hindering%20the%20growth%20of%20women-led%20businesses%20in%20India%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20micro-financing%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%